{"tid":1538222,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"已經估到真係撤回，中共同班建制會點攻擊我地，請諗定反擊","createTime":"2019-09-04T06:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T14:19:57.000Z","uid":161781,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ab08a457e670b6fe123cabed492acc6cd0db8e5c","tid":1538222,"uid":161781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:40:15.000Z","msg":"如果真係只係撤回，相信大家都唔會收貨<br />\n中共就可以將「變質」、「奪權」之類既字眼扣落運動到，令我地處於下風<br />\n（因為呢場係反送中運動，所以送中一撤，名義上，呢場運動就應完結）<br />\n大家應諗定反擊方法，例如雖然場運動以反送中為引線，但隨住運動進行，越來越多既問題被揭示，如警暴，所以五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n大家要料敵於先，唔好見步行步"},{"pid":"7b283026286eb5c9b53bdd233108e2ddcd68a108","tid":1538222,"uid":161781,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:41:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"48bcd0e6cf3f46eccec4e69db2163a38dbb4654b","tid":1538222,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:41:41.000Z","msg":"佢撤更加要全力宣傳<span style=\"color: red;\">點解</span>缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求吓大家，暫停鑽牛角尖睇多啲評論<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537499</a><br />\n<br />\n[緊急]如果共媒01係真，要全力推一國兩制失效同中英聯合聲明<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537880\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537880</a>"},{"pid":"b36127062f445efb11fd5343e6a959b472a046ba","tid":1538222,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:41:48.000Z","msg":"梗係主力打警暴啦"},{"pid":"1dfd65e192fd03203705902ef3e33b70dfef124f","tid":1538222,"uid":161781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:43:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fe88663a3c9a50f5b4bd79c319683e323f27b40","tid":1538222,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:43:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cWEMUHb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcWEMUHb.jpg&h=cc5ef0de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n入嚟幫手推<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n</span></span></strong> <br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a>"},{"pid":"8323e5a4175e101c4409e12c4288967cacd4b581","tid":1538222,"uid":261343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:44:18.000Z","msg":"又話唔可以撤回？<br />\n你叫班藍絲同黑警支持左你咁耐令到自己神憎鬼厭係為左咩野？<br />\n原來有暴徒先會聽市民講野<br />\n而且若果之前話唔可以撤回呢家又變可以既話<br />\n咁即係其餘四大訴求都應該可以由做唔到變做做到喇"},{"pid":"fdc04652cd381777a5b8e2a02dfd27728d4c0b5b","tid":1538222,"uid":55571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:45:32.000Z","msg":"早有準備好事嚟<br />\n集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade2cc245ad74e1387487fbfa7096c5182427428","tid":1538222,"uid":266569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:46:55.000Z","msg":"我正式宣布香港人要6大訴求, 要加埋解散現役警隊及重組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533820\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533820</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b47742cf6e4f7a0998a5c64e14b7b0d65435d9ad","tid":1538222,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:47:31.000Z","msg":"黑警食屎啦"},{"pid":"de628bf9ac0c726805dbea03833f2d3592ac21b5","tid":1538222,"uid":161781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:49:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0136e71f5af18d8a5d5c079f58b6b4c8230e5ab","tid":1538222,"uid":161781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:54:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76b4f788de164588c2c403084a840fc3c37a3feb","tid":1538222,"uid":100273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T06:55:10.000Z","msg":"準備文宣，將政府所有敗政列晒出黎，逃犯條例只係其中一項敗政，能夠阻止，只係我地好彩，其他不能被阻止ge就繼續禍港，但敗政頻生ge根本原因就係政制不公，意見不能有效公平地被採納"},{"pid":"89be686edb2732184e5907614306ae49af2a59b8","tid":1538222,"uid":531